0.3.0 - 2017-06-08
——————————————————————————————————
* Adds custom Redux reducer/state logic to `kit/lib/redux.js`
* Adds `seamless-immutable`, to ensure Redux state is immutable
* Updates `colour` reducer to use immutable data types
* Adds `redux-thunk`, for gaining access to `dispatch` function inside actions
* Adds `unwind` function, for unwrapping reducer/state objects

